      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# UI / Interaction Nodeset\n\nCandidate types from the source board:\n- `view`\n- `panel`\n- `control`\n- `state`\n- `binding`\n- `route`\n- `modal`\n- `layout-region`\n- `feedback`\n- `theme-token`\n\nThis family is appealing, but it risks collapsing into a generic UI builder unless the semantics stay sharp.",
