    {
      "id": "ui-interaction-membership-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Minimal UI Core",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": -90
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Minimal UI Core\n\nApprove in v1:\n- `view`\n- `panel`\n- `control`\n- `state`\n- `binding`\n- `route`\n\nDefer:\n- `modal`\n- `layout-region`\n- `feedback`\n- `theme-token`\n\nKeep v1 centered on structure and interaction semantics.",
        "_classBinding": {
