    {
      "id": "ui-interaction-dependency-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "UI Pressures",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": 320
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## UI Pressures\n\nLikely typed relationships:\n- `view` contains `panel`\n- `panel` contains `control`\n- `binding` binds `control` to `state`\n- `route` navigates to `view`\n\nRuntime pressure:\n- renderable regions\n- reactive state updates\n- navigable routes\n- summary views for large UI graphs\n\nStatus:\n- package root created\n- template created\n- class artifacts created\n- `ui-view` and `ui-state` keys used to avoid collisions with broader system vocabulary",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
